data.description: Welcome to 7423 Picnic Woods Road, a truly stunning residence nestled on a serene 5.82-acre lot in the heart of Middletown and the highly desirable Middletown School District! This home offers a perfect blend of luxurious living and natural beauty, providing a peaceful retreat for its fortunate occupants. As you approach, the eye-catching wrap-around decks immediately capture attention, offering breathtaking views from every room. The home boasts light-filled interiors with soaring ceilings, creating an inviting and open atmosphere throughout. The main level is a showcase of modern design and functionality. The family room features  a wall of windows and sliding glass doors that lead to the decks offering picturesque surroundings. This space effortlessly flows into the chef's kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops,  center island, a convenient breakfast bar, and a casual dining area. Access to the expansive wrap-around deck allows for seamless indoor-outdoor living. On the main level, discover a versatile space that can be utilized as a formal dining room or living room, a well-appointed bedroom, and a full bath. This level is designed to accommodate various lifestyle needs, providing flexibility and comfort. The upper level hosts two luxurious bedroom suites, each with its own en-suite full bath, walk-in closets, and balcony/deck access. The convenience of laundry facilities on this level adds to the overall functionality of the home. Ascend to the top level, where a spacious bedroom with cathedral ceilings awaits, complete with balcony access, a private office, and an additional loft area that could serve as another bedroom. The lower level is thoughtfully designed, featuring another bedroom, a full bath, and a versatile space ideal for a game room or exercise room. Ample storage ensures that every item has its place. The outdoor amenities are equally impressive, with two pastures, a grass riding ring, a dry lot, and a run-in for horses. Enjoy the above-ground saltwater pool and relax in the fenced backyard, creating a perfect oasis for entertaining or simply unwinding in the natural surroundings. Sellers are offering a $10,000 seller credit towards a 2:1 Interest buydown with a full price offer. Flyer uploaded in documents
